Feature: Interacting with tweets on twitter.com
  As I user I want to be able to interact with other user's tweets in specific ways:
  - liking tweets
  - retweeting
  - commenting on tweets
  - sharing tweets outside

  Scenario: Like a tweet on your wall
  Scenario: Retweet a tweet on your wall
  Scenario: Retweet a tweet on your wall with a comment
  Scenario: Comment on a tweet on your wall
  Scenario: Reply to an existing comment on a tweet
  Scenario: Send a tweet via a DM to another user
  Scenario: Add a tweet to bookmarks
  Scenario: Copy a link to a tweet
  Scenario: Report a tweet
  Scenario: Block an author of a tweet
  Scenario: Watch an author of a tweet
  Scenario: Move to the profile page of a tweet's author
